OL,5,Ctreatment
OL,7,FThe government has announced another
OL,8,Finterim payment of #210,000 for those
OL,9,Faffected by the contaminated blood
OL,10,Fscandal.
OL,12,FPayments are to made before the end of
OL,13,Fthe summer and its hoped full
OL,14,Fcompensation will be made before the
OL,15,Fend of the year.
OL,17,FHealth minister Robin Swann told the
OL,18,FAssembly today said there would be 'no
OL,19,Fpost code differential' in payments
OL,20,Fand any further delay would be another
OL,21,Ffailure.
