OL,5,Ctreatment
OL,7,FContaminated blood products exacted a
OL,8,Fheavy price from Hemophiliacs in
OL,9,FNorthern Ireland.
OL,11,FAt least 100 were infected with HIV or
OL,12,FHepatitis, condemned to death or a
OL,13,Flife of illness because of their
OL,14,Ftreatments.
OL,16,FMost came under the care of Dr
OL,17,FElizabeth Mayne at the Belfast
OL,18,FHemophilia Center in the 1970s and
OL,19,F1980s.
