OL,5,Ctreatment
OL,7,FThe Inquiry described her manner
OL,8,Ftoward her patients as "Paternalism
OL,9,Fwrit large".
OL,11,FDr Mayne was the doctor at the very
OL,12,Fcentre of the scandal in Northern
OL,13,FIreland - one of her patients was
OL,14,FAnthony O'Sullivan.
OL,16,FHis daughter Sinead told UTV: "She was
OL,17,Flike a mother figure to him, he
OL,18,Ftrusted her so much.
