OL,5,Ctreatment
OL,7,F"The whole family grew up talking
OL,8,Fabout her, knowing her, thinking she
OL,9,Fwas amazing..."
OL,11,FIn a clip of Dr Mayne filmed in 1976
OL,12,Fby UTV, she extols the virtues of a
OL,13,Fnew medical breakthrough - called
OL,14,FFactor 8 it was used to treat
OL,15,FCatherine Kerr's husband Neil.
OL,17,FBut Factor 8 was made from risky blood
OL,18,Fsources, and deadly diseases lurked
OL,19,Fwithin - HIV and Hepatitis.
