OL,7,FNeil raised safety concerns but Dr
OL,8,FMayne dismissed them.
OL,10,FIn the UTV archive footage, Dr Mayne
OL,11,Ftalked about it being a wonder
OL,12,Ftreatment and said "sometimes a little
OL,13,Fvirus does slip in".
OL,15,FCatherine said: "And patients paid
OL,16,Fwith their lives."
