OL,7,FCatherine added: "There's so much
OL,8,Fevidence now that they knew what they
OL,9,Fwere doing, they knew they were using
OL,10,Fcontaminated blood, I'll never forgive
OL,11,Fher."
OL,13,FSinead added: "She hurt so many
OL,14,Fpeople, not even just by giving the
OL,15,FFactor but how she treated them then
OL,16,Fand how she spoke to people and how
OL,17,Fshe spoke about people, she showed no
OL,18,Fremorse."
